@description.name: @description
@description.body: This widget provides a root widget for popups and tooltips if qooxdoo is used inside a traditional HTML page. Widgets placed into a page will overlay the HTML content. For this reason the widget's layout is initialized with an instance of {@link qx.ui.layout.Basic}. The widget's layout cannot be changed. The page widget does not support paddings and decorators with insets. Note: This widget does not support decorations! If you want to place widgets inside existing DOM elements use {@link qx.ui.root.Inline}.
